title: Magic Music Editor 5.3 (The Ultimate Music Editor)
description:
Friendly interface allows you to perform lots of different operations in an easy way. You can use it to record your own music, voice, or other audio, edit it, mix it with other audio or musical parts, add effects like reverb, chorus, and echo, and master it so that you can burn it to a CD, post it on the world wide Web, or E-mail it. Magic Music Editor supports all major audio file formats.

Version 5.3 may include unspecified updates, enhancements, or bug fixes.
